OL,3,CDangerous cladding still on 87 West
OL,4,CMidlands buildings
OL,6,FDangerous cladding is still to be
OL,7,Fremoved from 87 buildings across the
OL,8,FWest Midlands, figures show.
OL,10,FData from the West Midlands Combined
OL,11,FAuthority (WMCA) reveals that out of
OL,12,F273 buildings identified as unsafe
OL,13,Fafter the Grenfell disaster, 168 have
OL,14,Fnow had work completed.
OL,16,FRemediation is currently underway on
OL,17,Fanother 18. But that leaves 87
OL,18,Fbuildings where work hasn't yet
OL,19,Fstarted.
