OL,6,FOne of those affected is the Post Box
OL,7,Fapartments in Birmingham, where
OL,8,Fresidents found out in 2021 that the
OL,9,Fbuilding was lined with a potentially
OL,10,Fhighly flammable polystyrene
OL,11,Finsulation.
OL,13,FResident Colin Speller, who has lived
OL,14,Fthere since 2014, said: "The worry is
OL,15,Fthat a fire starting within a flat
OL,16,Fwould get into that insulation, spread
OL,17,Fupwards and sideways, and affect other
OL,18,Fflats.
