OL,6,F"We're not a high rise. We don't have
OL,7,Fthe plastic on the outside, but the
OL,8,Frisk is perceived to be within those
OL,9,Fwalls, within that insulation, and
OL,10,Fthat is what has got to be replaced.
OL,12,F"The developer has agreed to make this
OL,13,Fbuilding safe, but in the meantime,
OL,14,Fresidents are left in limbo. You can't
OL,15,Fsell your flat, so even if you wanted
OL,16,Fto move, you probably couldn't.
