OL,6,F"It will be fixed, but it'll be over a
OL,7,Flong period of time. They told us
OL,8,Frecently that we're looking at a
OL,9,Fhorizon of about three years...So
OL,10,Fwe're looking at 2028 at the very
OL,11,Fearliest."
OL,13,FIn response to the delays, the WMCA
OL,14,Fhas launched a new West Midlands
OL,15,FRemediation Acceleration Plan to speed
OL,16,Fup the removal of unsafe cladding.
