OL,6,FIt follows recommendations from the
OL,7,FGrenfell Inquiry, which called on
OL,8,FMayoral Combined Authorities to bring
OL,9,Ftogether councils, fire services and
OL,10,Fother partners to tackle the issue.
OL,12,FRichard Parker, Mayor of the West
OL,13,FMidlands, said: "I've listened to
OL,14,Fheartbreaking stories from residents
OL,15,Fabout the impact living in an unsafe
OL,16,Fbuilding is having on their lives.
OL,18,F"The Grenfell Tower tragedy must
OL,19,Falways remain in our minds as a stark
OL,20,Fexample of what can happen when safety
OL,21,Fis not put first.
