OL,6,F"That's why we've been working with
OL,7,Fpartner agencies to get the
OL,8,Fremediation process sped up, so we can
OL,9,Fensure nothing like this ever happens
OL,10,Fagain. Everyone deserves a safe home."
OL,12,FArea Commander Gemma McSweeney, Head
OL,13,Fof Protection at West Midlands Fire
OL,14,FService, said: "Residents' safety is
OL,15,Fat the heart of everything we do.
