OL,6,F"We know the impact unsafe buildings
OL,7,Fcan have on residents and communities,
OL,8,Fwhich is why the Remediation
OL,9,FAcceleration Plan is a vital step in
OL,10,Fmaking sure dangerous cladding is
OL,11,Fremoved at pace.
OL,13,F"We remain focused on ensuring
OL,14,Fcompliance and, by working closely
OL,15,Fwith our partners, we can give
OL,16,Fresidents greater reassurance, so they
OL,17,Ffeel safe in their homes."
